postData.readme:
# Hash String

[![NPM](https://nodei.co/npm/hash-string.png)](https://nodei.co/npm/hash-string/)

A string hashing function based on Daniel J. Bernstein's popular 'times 33' hash algorithm.

## Example

```javascript
console.log(hash('{ test: true }'));
```
